    <center><table class="itemDisplayTable">
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Title:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">A Study on Performance Appraisal at National Thermal Power Corporation (NTPC) Ltd.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Authors:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Supriya Anjali Bharti</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Keywords:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Performance Appraisal<br />National Thermal Power Corporation</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Issue Date:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">May-2011 </td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Publisher:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">SRM University</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Series/Report no.:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">P5320</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Abstract:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">I take immense pleasure presenting this project report on performance Appraisal in National
Thermal Power Corporation (NTPC) Ltd, PATNA. This project intended to fulfill the
requirement for the completion of MBA Degree. The real objective behind the practical
training &amp; preparation of project report is to gain exposure is to actual work environment and
blend required theoretical knowledge towards facilitation of its application. In Professional
course like, Management practical training and close contact with prevailing system in the
organization is of great importance.
During Course of training in my Specialization Personnel, I had an opportunity to apply
theoretical knowledge to the real field of personnel.
In the course of my training, I found that a part from theoretical knowledge in the field of
personnel, a manager must follow tailor made approach based on his understanding of an
action, attitudes needs and urges of the workers concerned.
This implies that individual in an organization can’t be treated alike employing people with
different psychological frame work is really a difficult job.
I have chosen the topic of my study “performance appraisal”, because it is a vital part
of personnel department. In preparing this report care has been taken to make it
comprehensive and reliable to the extent possible. This report care has been prepared and
arranged under Heads and Subheads. I had tried to gather all relevant important facts
regarding this topic to my best efforts.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">URI:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/9589">http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/9589</a></td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Appears in Collections:</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="/dspace/handle/123456789/8329">MBA-2011</a><br/></td></tr>
</table></center><br/>
